"I loved it," she said of her return and short time in the Rumble. "I was waiting to find out when my surprise return would be, for months. The Royal Rumble was perfect. Just the way the entire day came together and those five seconds will live on forever. I think it was the perfect way to comeback."

Green would then confirm she had been signed for months.

When asked if the delay was trying to figure out her character, Green replied, "I think so, and a matter of, 'when is the perfect opportunity to put her in?
